# Form submissions are sent to your email via Formspree.
# 1. Sign up at https://formspree.io (free)
# 2. Create a new form and set the email where you want to receive submissions
# 3. Copy your form ID from the form's endpoint (e.g. xjweqlze from https://formspree.io/f/xjweqlze)
# 4. Copy this file to .env and set your form ID:
VITE_FORMSPREE_ID=your_form_id_here
